author: hustla187
title: At Least These Appeared in One Set
review: I'm not a fan of Spongebob Lego sets, but I do praise Lego for making the Space suit minifigures as magnets because those only appeared in one set. Now, Spongebob, Sandy, and Patrick can explore undiscovered lands on your fridge. 5 out of 5.

author: mvila09
title: "It's pretty impressive all right"-Spongebob in Sandy's Rocket.
review: My sister wanted this set the first time she saw it.So,my mom bought it for her and I'm reviewing it.This set includes a space suit Spongebob and Patrick,and Sandy.You also get a jelly fish,net,and a flag.Pros:Space suit Spongebob has some nice details,Space suit Patrick is cool and fun to play with,Sandy is not really bad but not really good,She has some nice details like her teeth,Cool helmet but it's missing something,yellow magnets.Cons:Where's the flower on Sandy's helmet?That's the only Con but it's alright.****4 stars.
